      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "假设要给几座村庄铺电缆，让它们全都连通。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "每段线路都有造价，我们想让总花费尽可能少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "这就是最小生成树问题：用最省的成本连通所有点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-1",
      "filename": "tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "生成树是一组边，连通全部节点却不含任何环。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-2",
      "filename": "tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "n 个节点的生成树，恰好有 n 减 1 条边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "tree",
      "line_id": "tree-3",
      "filename": "tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/tree-tree-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "权重之和最小的那一棵，就叫最小生成树。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "kruskal",
      "line_id": "krus-1",
      "filename": "kruskal-krus-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/kruskal-krus-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "Kruskal 先把所有边按权重从小到大排好队。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "kruskal",
      "line_id": "krus-2",
      "filename": "kruskal-krus-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/kruskal-krus-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "依次尝试加入最便宜的边，只要它不会围成环。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "kruskal",
      "line_id": "krus-3",
      "filename": "kruskal-krus-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/kruskal-krus-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "判断成环靠并查集：两端已在同一集合就跳过。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "prim",
      "line_id": "prim-1",
      "filename": "prim-prim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/minimum-spanning-tree/xiaoxiao/prim-prim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "Prim 换个思路，从任意一个节点开始生长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "minimum-spanning-tree",
      "section_id": "prim",
      "line_id": "prim-2",
